Jul 14, 2025
Release Notes
Recent Update

A new parameter called EP Offset was added, allowing the user to dynamically control the entry level (Entry Price). If set to 0, the entry is placed at the edge of the 6:00 PM NY candle (Low for BUY, High for SELL). If the value is greater than zero, the EP is calculated as a percentage of the candle’s range, simulating intermediate levels similar to Fibonacci. This logic has been implemented in both the indicator and the strategy (backtest) versions.
